Cole Slaw
=========

Ingredients:
------------

- 1/4 tsp salt
- 4 cups grated cabbage
- 4 tbsp sugar
- 2 tbsp vinegar
- 1/2 cup Hellmans mayonnaise
- 1 tsp celery seed

Preparation:
------------

Mix salt, sugar, vinegar, mayonnaise, & celery seed together in small bowl.
Pour over grated cabbage.

